org.projecthaystack.server

Class BMPServer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.projecthaystack.HProj
      • org.projecthaystack.server.HServer
        • org.projecthaystack.server.BMPServer
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BMPHaystackServer

    public abstract class BMPServer
extends HServer
    BMPServer is the interface between HServlet and a database of tag based entities. All methods on BMPServer must be thread safe. It extends HServer to add additional abstract operation for BMPHaystackServer to implement.
